ing-ramadan-itikaf\/","url_meta":{"origin":15820,"position":0},"title":"Imam al-Nawawi on Spiritual Retreat in Ramadan, al-I\u2019tikaf","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 14, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"\"The Prophet seeks seclusion in the last ten nights.\"","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Hadith Chapters \u0623\u0628\u0648\u0627\u0628 \u0627\u0644\u062d\u062f\u064a\u062b&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Hadith Chapters \u0623\u0628\u0648\u0627\u0628 \u0627\u0644\u062d\u062f\u064a\u062b","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/category\/hadith-chapters\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14792,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/an-nawawi-friday-prayer-jumuah-jummah\/","url_meta":{"origin":15820,"position":1},"title":"Imam al-Nawawi on Friday Prayer, Salat al-Jumu&#8217;ah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 23, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"\"Verily, the best of your days is Friday.\"","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Hadith Chapters \u0623\u0628\u0648\u0627\u0628 \u0627\u0644\u062d\u062f\u064a\u062b&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Hadith Chapters \u0623\u0628\u0648\u0627\u0628 \u0627\u0644\u062d\u062f\u064a\u062b","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/category\/hadith-chapters\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15886,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/manners-etiquette-and-traditions-of-eid\/","url_meta":{"origin":15820,"position":2},"title":"Manners, Etiquette, and Traditions for Eid","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 26, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"\"May Allah accept good deeds from us and you.\"","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sunnah \u0627\u0644\u0633\u0646\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sunnah \u0627\u0644\u0633\u0646\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/category\/sunnah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":21111,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/fasting-muharram-day-of-ashura\/","url_